  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join Discord!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Sometimes the best therapy is a long drive with music\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/6f9c4d88f740001ffcff2593c7c2c6bd.poster.avif?t=1743269133\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/6f9c4d88f740001ffcff2593c7c2c6bd.webm?t=1743269133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/6f9c4d88f740001ffcff2593c7c2c6bd.mp4?t=1743269133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/1210f8ca5926e12b5dbf53099a631a71.poster.avif?t=1743269133\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/1210f8ca5926e12b5dbf53099a631a71.webm?t=1743269133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/1210f8ca5926e12b5dbf53099a631a71.mp4?t=1743269133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Open World</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drive day & night, pick up hitchhikers, refuel, check engine temperature. Watch out for the cops!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/10d9986b4cc9373af72ec9970a831f13.poster.avif?t=1743269133\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/10d9986b4cc9373af72ec9970a831f13.webm?t=1743269133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/10d9986b4cc9373af72ec9970a831f13.mp4?t=1743269133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Driving jobs</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Taxi, Bus, Trucks and much more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/ed336128261278ce0c5b24cf44b0f29c.poster.avif?t=1743269133\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/ed336128261278ce0c5b24cf44b0f29c.webm?t=1743269133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/ed336128261278ce0c5b24cf44b0f29c.mp4?t=1743269133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Realistic Tire Physics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With sophisticated vehicle and tire physics, you can enjoy realistic and challenging driving. Feel the tire grip and burn some tires by drifting! If you are a keyboard player, don't forget to use 'Burnout' when you want to let the rear go sideways. Driving Assist is available for keyboard players and controllers are fully supported. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Singleplayer and Multiplayer Mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy solitude in single-player or have fun with friends in multiplayer mode.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Time attack</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The online leaderboard shows you how fast you are. Autocross is a good way to improve your driving skills.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Race</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can compete with other players on the on-road and off-road tracks, or you can set waypoints and open a street race event.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Company</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create a company and make your own bus/truck route.<br>Hire an AI driver or other player to work for you.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open world (24 x 16 Km) with Day & Night cycle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ Cars, Trucks and Trailers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Driving with Keyboard, Mouse, Gamepad, Steering wheel</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Realistic, yet easy (with the assist feature) driving </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Single-player and Multiplayer Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Passenger Transportation (Hitchhikers, Taxi, Bus) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Cargo Transportation (Pickup, Trucks, Semi-Trailer)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Special Vehicle Jobs (Police, Tow Truck, Ambulance and more will be added) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Refueling</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Replacing car parts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Buying/Renting cars</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Blinker, Headlight, Horn, Driving Mode, and Auto-Pilot!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Race</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Time attack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Autocross</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Online leaderboards</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Sometimes the best therapy is a long drive with music\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/6f9c4d88f740001ffcff2593c7c2c6bd.poster.avif?t=1743269133\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/6f9c4d88f740001ffcff2593c7c2c6bd.webm?t=1743269133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/6f9c4d88f740001ffcff2593c7c2c6bd.mp4?t=1743269133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/1210f8ca5926e12b5dbf53099a631a71.poster.avif?t=1743269133\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/1210f8ca5926e12b5dbf53099a631a71.webm?t=1743269133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/1210f8ca5926e12b5dbf53099a631a71.mp4?t=1743269133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Open World</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drive day & night, pick up hitchhikers, refuel, check engine temperature. Watch out for the cops!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/10d9986b4cc9373af72ec9970a831f13.poster.avif?t=1743269133\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/10d9986b4cc9373af72ec9970a831f13.webm?t=1743269133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/10d9986b4cc9373af72ec9970a831f13.mp4?t=1743269133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Driving jobs</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Taxi, Bus, Trucks and much more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/ed336128261278ce0c5b24cf44b0f29c.poster.avif?t=1743269133\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/ed336128261278ce0c5b24cf44b0f29c.webm?t=1743269133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1369670/extras/ed336128261278ce0c5b24cf44b0f29c.mp4?t=1743269133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Realistic Tire Physics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With sophisticated vehicle and tire physics, you can enjoy realistic and challenging driving. Feel the tire grip and burn some tires by drifting! If you are a keyboard player, don't forget to use 'Burnout' when you want to let the rear go sideways. Driving Assist is available for keyboard players and controllers are fully supported. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Singleplayer and Multiplayer Mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy solitude in single-player or have fun with friends in multiplayer mode.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Time attack</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The online leaderboard shows you how fast you are. Autocross is a good way to improve your driving skills.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Race</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can compete with other players on the on-road and off-road tracks, or you can set waypoints and open a street race event.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Company</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create a company and make your own bus/truck route.<br>Hire an AI driver or other player to work for you.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open world (24 x 16 Km) with Day & Night cycle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ Cars, Trucks and Trailers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Driving with Keyboard, Mouse, Gamepad, Steering wheel</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Realistic, yet easy (with the assist feature) driving </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Single-player and Multiplayer Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Passenger Transportation (Hitchhikers, Taxi, Bus) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Cargo Transportation (Pickup, Trucks, Semi-Trailer)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Special Vehicle Jobs (Police, Tow Truck, Ambulance and more will be added) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Refueling</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Replacing car parts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Buying/Renting cars</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Blinker, Headlight, Horn, Driving Mode, and Auto-Pilot!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Race</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Time attack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Autocross</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Online leaderboards</p></li></ul>",
